&lt;li&gt;Help define and own Moloco&#39;s employee communications strategy, leading the day-to-day of our global internal communications programs and evolving the function as the company scales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with senior leaders on change communications, building clear narratives, toolkits, and cascades that drive understanding across a globally distributed team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement internal communications programs that connect employees across regions and reinforce culture and strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on high-stakes internal communications: executive messages, company announcements, town hall remarks, and sensitive employee-facing content.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish channel governance and communication standards across platforms, with clear guidance on when and how to use each.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build measurement for internal communications effectiveness, tracking reach, clarity, and engagement to continuously improve how we communicate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and prepare executives for internal moments, including talking points, message alignment, and delivery guidance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with recruiting and onboarding teams to ensure new hires understand Moloco&#39;s culture, values, and story from day one.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate cultural and regulatory differences in communications approaches across North America, EMEA, APAC, and other key regions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anticipate issues and coordinate across Communications, Legal, and People to ensure timely, accurate, and trusted employee communications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How Do I Know if the Role is Right For Me?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8-10 years of strategic communications experience with significant experience leading internal or employee communications at a high-growth or public company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record building or transforming an internal communications function, with clear impact on alignment, culture, and employee understanding.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional writing and editing skills; able to translate complex business strategy into clear, human communication for a globally distributed, technically diverse workforce.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience leading change communications and company-wide forums in partnership with People, Legal, and Finance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong executive presence and coaching ability; comfortable preparing senior leaders for high-visibility internal moments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;International communications experience with demonstrated understanding of how cultural and regional differences shape employee communication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High judgment and discretion, with experience navigating sensitive communications in a fast-moving, high-stakes environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI fluency and curiosity: as an AI company, we expect our communications leaders to actively explore how new tools and practices can make the function smarter and faster.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation &amp;amp; Benefits &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;U.S.-based employees have access to medical, dental, and vision insurance, a 401(k) plan with company match, short-term and long-term disability coverage, basic life insurance, and well-being benefits and perks. U.S.-based employees also receive up to 12 scheduled paid holidays per calendar year and one Thrive Day off per quarter. Additionally, all employees have Flexible Time Off (FTO).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The successful candidate may be eligible for a bonus and equity awards. Eligibility and amounts are determined by performance and the terms of the applicable plans. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The location for this role is listed above. For base pay range purposes, location-based compensation is grouped into the following regions. Your region is determined by your assigned work location.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Region A: &lt;/strong&gt;Menlo Park Office, New York Office, SF Bay Area, New York Metro Area&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Region B:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Seattle Office, Seattle, Los Angeles/Orange County, San Diego, Austin, Boston, Washington DC Metro Area, Miami&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
